Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:07.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.42,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.50,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是這個沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:15.59,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:20.01,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:24.02,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是個圍裙男孩
